Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.46,0:24:27.25,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0\fs41}Dear My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.39,0:24:32.09,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0\fsp-4}すぐそばに行くわ
