Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.95,0:23:41.49,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}那个约定的小山上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.11,0:23:50.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}月光之下吻着鲜艳欲滴的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:54.20,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}那把钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:58.12,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}通向不思议之国度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:03.22,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}紧紧攥着它的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.29,0:24:07.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}无法长大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:14.52,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}没有什么值得害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:22.89,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}你绝不是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.39,0:24:32.09,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}我会立刻来到你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.53,0:24:36.33,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}无论你在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.53,0:24:39.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}我们都紧紧相连
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.22,0:24:49.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}我会立刻将你紧紧拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.58,0:24:54.47,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}沉睡在臂腕中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.86,0:25:00.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,1500)\be0}别再哭泣了
