Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是不是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么神灵们会这么慌乱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在害怕  被同伴孤立了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉比之前看到时小了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.62,0:00:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要带上它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.23,0:00:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡…匡幸  武器  武器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不行  不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据气象局预报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台风11号正位于津岛西南方120公里\N海洋面以时速70公里迅速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中心区域保持着最大风速40米的强势
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果照这样登录北九州  与过去的台风10号…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎  这边也要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…抱歉  那边也能帮我弄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  连慧都过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的台风好像很厉害啊  我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边不要紧  男人变多了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴风雨对我们来说到是有利的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神会救我们之类的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那个宗教团体最近强迫水天镇一个女孩成为了新教祖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那个教祖说  最近龙神会降临到这个村子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎  衣服的尺寸我回去改一下  一会儿穿起来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去准备自己的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平田医生  要搭我的车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事必须向古森你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理诊疗  是为了我的研究而做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧  憎恶和记忆的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为扁桃体和海马体间的系统存在缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我想古森会不会是第一个克服这种缺陷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治疗我很认真  但动机不纯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈是多亏了医生您而精神起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且医生来到这边后  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想弄清楚我脑中的异变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:05:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环境对脑产生的影响  这是我的新目标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你让我听
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我在听这些录音时见到了古森的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然这是意识变异的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但姐姐对那时的古森说了一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在幽世和梦里都没能见到姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这一定有什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  一定有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  如果是古森一定能救出都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能做这点小事  很抱歉其他的都帮不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是水天镇宗教法人  大神拜灵会的门口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据村民们的证言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在该团体的代表  竟然是一位小学生的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能聚集这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人工生命体…都死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种说法真不象你的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,培养素都清理干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但计划的流水线上还是制造了一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是初期  但实验性的生产已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么多…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照上面的指示  应该会作暂时的废弃处理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中岛先生  虽然不该我说  但能请你去把你太太接回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡幸他很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家请看  在水天町的田地之间架起了无数的鸟居
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村民们真的相信龙神会降临这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我确实也对大神大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但原则上是政教分离的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈  铃木大叔可真能干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  已经过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道男  就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  等一会儿会把你带回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  已经来了吗  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在此时  有一位身穿和服像母亲的女性带着一个小女孩打算进入
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  这不是很合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定行  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋  别笑啦  多对不起太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算进得去  之后才是关键吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量的神灵开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底会发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我不知道创造生命是否是允许人类进行的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果没有这种觉悟就动手  会变成什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人类创造的你们也是我们的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:11:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边也被媒体缠住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…加畑老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  在现世看不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从葛城过来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵照一言主神的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这孩子来侍奉大神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但请你们改日再来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能突然潜进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  那我跟道男就来佯动作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神什么的不会出现啦  对吧  阿荣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨好大  快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？好象能看见什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…  龙神  是龙神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神  龙神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  是龙神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神  龙神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量也太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙…龙…龙神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家怎么了  明明什么都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得太过分了吧  道男
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都  你不能留在这里  跟我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驹玖珠先生已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在铃木先生去接他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  快点  都不能待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神出现了  如大神大人所言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再也感觉不到悲伤和厌恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实没有我的存在会更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都就是都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是其他任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都  对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千帆  别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个男孩进了大神大人的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从玄关进入正面突破会不会太难？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从后面就没有逃走的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可以逃走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去内房  关禁闭时我曾被关在里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不能打架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是同伴  你只是跟大家稍有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…龙神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间里有一个茶箱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前就已经挖好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们的祖先想用这个暗道做什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一片漆黑什么都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没关系对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:18:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在让大神大人被带走  好像不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要帮我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎  找机会逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子就应该乖乖听大人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这上面清楚的留着你的指纹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个杀死了那个男人会怎么样  你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法  那就要教育一下了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们晚了点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能等待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我多点勇气  那孩子也不会遇到这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么  榆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  你们是同伴  好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不会被同伴孤立了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  都  都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  别再逞强了  你我都是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微吓吓他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道男呀  你都干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我都那么努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的  骗你的  成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是大神大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:21:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能再见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在幽世守护着太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足够了  就算你不那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.59,0:22:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.83,0:23:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐跟我成为一体了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.79,0:23:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐跟我成为一体  现在也还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像都最初把我看成光  我也确实感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  都
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.75,0:24:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}信  你也来笑一个
